## [Lists](https://shd101wyy.github.io/markdown-preview-enhanced/#/markdown-basics?id=lists)

**无序列表**
- item 1
- item 2
  - item 2-1
  - item 2-2
    - item 2-2-1

**有序列表**
1. item 1
1. item 2
    1. item 2-1
    3. item 2-2
        1. item 2-2-1

> 注：有序列表中的序号与编写markdown中给定的需要无关

## [Fenced code block](https://shd101wyy.github.io/markdown-preview-enhanced/#/markdown-basics?id=fenced-code-block)

**语法高亮**
```ruby
require 'redcarpet'
markdown = Redcarpet.new("Hello World!")
puts markdown.to_html
```

**添加 class**
```javascript {.line-numbers, highlight=[1, 4-6]}
function add(x, y) {
  a = x;
  b = y;
  c = a + b;
  d = a * b;
  e = c + d;
  return e;
}
```
